Are you overwhelmed by feelings of sadness, rejection, betrayal, anger? Are you lonely, fearful, frustrated? Does your ex still have the power to push your buttons? In Divorce Zen, former divorce lawyer William Henry draws on his former clients as well as his own divorce experience and explains how escaping the misery of divorce requires a radical shift in mindset. He uncovers techniques that will help you to conquer your thoughts and emotions rather than being ruled by them, how to take back control of your emotional well-being, strengthen your inner resources and so much more. Reach Publishers, R225, available from Exclusive Books, Takealot and all good bookshops. 